dc_description_s: This data represents recreation areas and water access points for Wood County, Wisconsin in 2018 and includes the layers 'Wood_Recreation_Areas_2018' and 'Wood_Water_Access_2018'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2019. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2018. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2019.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://opendata.woodcogis.com/
